== Backdoor ==

A secure backdoor for concrete5. Login as any user from an external location.

Place the public keys in 'config/backdoor'.

This is only the server. Logging in requires a backdoor client. The client can be
downloaded from http://www.github.com/jasny/backdoor/client 

For more information see http://www.jasny.net/articles/a-secure-backdoor-for-php

